data.description: Exciting Opportunity: *PREFERRED LENDER OFFERING $14,000 IN DOWNPAYMENT AND CLOSING COST GRANTS! NO REPAYMENT REQUIRED, MUST QUALIFY*Ideal First Home at a Great Price - Act Quickly! This residence boasts an Inviting Open Floor Plan with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a versatile flex room. Interior was freshly painted approximately one year ago, exuding a modern feel. Positioned on a spacious corner lot, this property catches the eye. Great Location with easy access to I75. Notably, Solar Panels grace the roof, offering a host of advantages. Unleash your creativity in crafting the interior to your liking. Seize the moment to claim ownership of this extraordinary home! Professional Photos will be uploaded soon!
